	(500,'STARS 0.5 & 0.4','2010-02-18 16:00:07',32,'<p>AASHE released STARS 0.5 in April 2008.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/files/documents/STARS/STARS_0.5.pdf\" target=\"_self\">STARS 0.5</a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/STARS_0.5_Feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Feedback on STARS 0.5</a> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>AASHE released STARS 0.4 in September 2007.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"spaced_list\"><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/files/documents/STARS/STARS0.4.pdf\" target=\"_self\">STARS 0.4</a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li class=\"spaced_list\"><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/files/documents/STARS/STARS0.4commentsv2.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Comments on STARS 0.4</a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li class=\"spaced_list\"><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/files/documents/STARS/STARS0.4_survey_responses.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Responses to STARS 0.4 Survey</a> (pdf)<a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/stars/calls.php\" target=\"_self\"><br /> </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong>STARS Focus Calls</strong></h2>\r\n<p>AASHE held a series of focused conference calls from October through December 2007.&nbsp; These calls were intended for Strategic and Technical Advisory Committee members as well as invited experts.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Curriculum</strong> (Monday, October 29, 2007, 11:45-12:45 PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/curriculum_agenda102907.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/curriculum_call1029.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Summary notes</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Investment</strong> (Monday, November 12, 2007, 2-3 PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/investment_agenda111207.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/investment_notes111207.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Summary notes</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>E