enda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/Transportation_Call_Notes_11.30.07.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Summary notes</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Water &amp; Landscaping</strong> (Monday, December 3, 2007, 1-2 PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/water_landscaping_agenda120307.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Facilities</strong> (Tuesday, December 4, 2007, 9-10 PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/facilities_feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Feedback</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/facilities_agenda120407.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Research</strong> (Wednesday, December 5, 2007, 11-noon PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/research_feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Feedback</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/research_agenda120507.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/Research_Notes12.05.07.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Summary notes</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Co-curricular Education</strong> (Thursday, December 6, 2007, noon&ndash;1 PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/co-curricular_feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Feedback</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/co-curricula_agenda120607.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/Co-curricular_Call_Notes_12.6.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Summary notes</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Affordability &amp; Social Mobility</strong> (Tuesday, December 11, 2007, 1-2 PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"www.aashe.org/documents/stars/affordability_feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Feedback</em></a> (pdf)</em></li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/affordability_agenda121107.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em>Call was canceled due to low attendance</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Fair Labor</strong> (Wednesday, December 12, 2007, 1-2 PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/labor_feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Feedback</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/labor_agenda121207.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Sustainability Officers</strong> (Thursday, December 13, 2007, 9-10 PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/sustainability_officer_feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Feedback</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/officers_agenda121307.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/Call_Notes_Sust_Officer_12.13.07.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Summary notes</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Community Service</strong> (Friday, December 14, 2007, 11&ndash;noon PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/service_feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Feedback</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/service_agenda121407.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em>Call was canceled due to low attendance</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Sustainability Literacy</strong> (Monday, December 17, 2007, noon-1 PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/literacy_feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Feedback</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/literacy_agenda121707.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Diversity</strong> (Tuesday, December 18, 2007, 11-noon PST)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/diversity_feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><em>Feedback</em></a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/diversity_agenda121807.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Agenda</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><em><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/Diversity_Call_Notes_12.18.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Summary notes</a></em> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,'stars-05-and-04','<p>AASHE released STARS 0.5 in April 2008.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/files/documents/STARS/STARS_0.5.pdf\" target=\"_self\">STARS 0.5</a> (pdf)</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/documents/stars/STARS_0.5_Feedback.pdf\" target=\"_self\">Feedback on STARS 0.5</a> (pdf)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>AASHE released STARS 0.4 in September 2007.&nbsp;</p>',4599,'2013-08-01 11:39:54'),
	(100,'Why Participate?','2010-03-01 16:16:56',34,'<p>There are many <a href=\"https://stars.aashe.org/pages/get-involved/stars-participant-benefits.html\" target=\"_self\">benefits</a> associated with becoming a STARS Participant. According to STARS Participants, here are the top ten reasons to register:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1)  Earn Recognition for Sustainability Efforts on Your Campus</br>\r\n2)  Save Time and Money in Developing a Sustainability Report or Plan</br>\r\n3)  Streamline Reporting on Your Campus by Using Common Metrics</br>\r\n4)  Use STARS as a Guide to Set Goals and Generate New Ideas</strong></br>\r\n5)  STARS Requires Collaborate Across Campus for Data Collection</br>\r\n6)  Adopt STARS as a Teaching and Learning Tool</br>\r\n7)  Ability to Shape the STARS System by Providing Feedback</br>\r\n8)  Access STARS Resources in the \'My Resources\' Section of the STARS Reporting Tool</br>\r\n9)  Benchmark Your STARS Report with Peers</br>\r\n10)  Easily Communicate Your Achievements by Sharing Your STARS Report</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\r\n<p>Benefits of becoming a STARS Participant include, but are not limited to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Access to the online <strong>STARS Reporting Tool</strong>, which includes:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -<strong> Data synchronization</strong> with other specific rating and ranking organizations<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - <strong>Automated point calculation</strong> for each STARS credit<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -<strong> PDF Exports</strong> of Submission Data<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Ability to <strong>share data </strong>with other organizations outside of AASHE<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - <strong>Continuous access </strong>to update data<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Option to give <strong>multiple users access</strong> to the STARS Report<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -<strong> Data tracking resources</strong><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -<strong> STARS seal</strong> <strong>logo</strong><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>- Email templates</strong><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Template <strong>press release</strong><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - <strong>Promotional tools</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Earn a STARS rating and <strong>be recognized as a STARS rated institution</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Publicly posted STARS Report</strong> on the STARS website</li>\r\n<li>Full access to&nbsp;<strong>STARS Data Displays</strong></li>\r\n<li>Opportunities to <strong>influence STARS technical development</strong></li>\r\n<li>Inclusion in <strong>STARS Quarterly Review</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Free admission</strong> to STARS webinars</li>\r\n<li>And more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>View a printable version of the STARS Participant <a href=\"http://www.aashe.org/files/documents/STARS/benefits_of_participating_in_stars_final.pdf\" target=\"_self\">benefits</a> (pdf).</p>',1,'why-participate','',4740,'2013-08-08 08:11:37');
