ng\" border=\"0\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Multiple User   Accounts</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" align=\"center\">\r\n<p><img src=\"/media/static/images/accept.png\" border=\"0\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" align=\"center\">\r\n<p><img src=\"/media/static/images/accept.png\" border=\"0\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Option to allow other   organizations access to STARS and supplemental data</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" align=\"center\">\r\n<p><img src=\"/media/static/images/accept.png\" border=\"0\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" align=\"center\">\r\n<p><img src=\"/media/static/images/accept.png\" border=\"0\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>',1,'data-collector-benefits','<p>See a table that outlines the benefits associated with being a registered  STARS Participant and Campus Sustainability Data Collector Survey  Respondent.&nbsp; View additional information about <a href=\"/pages/get-involved/stars-participant-benefits.html\" target=\"_self\">STARS Participant benefits</a>.</p>',NULL,'2013-02-07 11:29:36'),
	(250,'Data Collector Registration','2012-02-07 11:00:48',79,'<p>AASHE has created the <a href=\"/pages/get-involved/campus-sustainability-data-collector/campus-sustainability-data-collector.html\" target=\"_self\">Campus Sustainability Data Collector</a> for   institutions not yet participating in STARS. Institutions that <a href=\"http://stars.aashe.org/register/\" target=\"_self\">register</a> for the Campus Sustainability Data Collector are referred to as  Survey  Respondents. This basic tool allows any higher education  institution  the option to share campus sustainability data with The  Princeton  Review and Sierra Magazine. Please note, the Sustainable Endowments Institute has <a href=\"http://greenreportcard.org/media\" target=\"_self\">suspended</a> the production of the College Sustainability Report Card and will no longer be seeking data for this publication. The  Data Collector is modeled after the STARS Reporting Tool  and is  available at no cost. However, this option does not include any  of the <a href=\"/pages/get-involved/campus-sustainability-data-collector/data-collector-benefits.html\" target=\"_self\">benefits</a> of the STARS Reporting Tool or those associated with being a STARS Participant.</p>\r\n<p>The Campus Sustainability Data Collector is simply a place to upload sustainability data. This information is not available to the public and institutions that use the Data Collector will not receive any recognition through STARS. Please note, The Princeton Review and Sierra magazine each have a different target audience and therefore may not include data from all institutions in their various publications.</p>\r\n<table class=\"thin\" style=\"width: 650px; height: 0px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" align=\"center\">\r\n<p><strong>Step by Step</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" align=\"center\">\r\n<p><strong>Survey Respondent</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>1. <a href=\"/register/\" target=\"_self\">Register</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Go to stars.aashe.org   and register for the Campus Sustainability Data Collector (no payment is   required)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>2. Data   collection</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Use the Campus   Sustainability Data Collector to input data</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>3. Share your   data</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Select   organizations that you want to share your data with</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>4. Submit</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Submit data (does   not go public)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>',1,'data-collector-registration','<table class=\"thin\" style=\"width: 550px; height: 126px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" align=\"center\">\r\n<p><strong>Step by Step</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" align=\"center\">\r\n<p><strong>Survey Respondent</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>1. <a href=\"/register/\" target=\"_self\">Register</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Go to stars.aashe.org   and register for the Campus Sustainability Data Collector (no payment is   required)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>2. Data   collection</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Use the Campus   Sustainability Data Collector to input data</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>3. Share your   data</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Select   organizations that you want to share your data with</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>4. Submit</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>Submit data (does   not go public)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>',NULL,'2012-04-02 14:48:57'),
