	(0,'Media Coverage Archive','2013-08-09 08:56:47',121,'<p>This archive contains <a href=\"#national_press\" target=\"_self\">national press</a>, <a href=\"#campus_articles\" target=\"_self\">articles in campus newspapers and on campus websites</a>, <a href=\"#blog_posts\" target=\"_self\">blog posts</a>, <a href=\"#press_releases\" target=\"_self\">press releases</a>, and <a href=\"#other\" target=\"_self\">other</a> media coverage of STARS that has occurred more than a year ago.&nbsp; The articles are listed below. For a complete list of more up-to-date articles, please visit our <a href=\"https://stars.aashe.org/pages/news-events/media-coverage.html\" target=\"_self\">Media Coverage</a> page.</p>\r\n<h3><a name=\"national_press\" target=\"_self\"></a>Articles in National, Regional, and Local Press</h3>\r\n<h4>May 2012</h4>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.facilitiesnet.com/green/tip/What-is-the-STARS-Rating-System--25275\" target=\"_self\">What is the STARS Rating System?</a></p>\r\n<h4>April 2012</h4>\r\n<p class=\"title\"><a href=\"http://www.ithacaindy.com/201204191097/Ithaca-College/Ithaca-College-Named-A-Top-Green-College\" target=\"_self\">Ithaca College Named A Top \'Green College\'</a><br /><a href=\"https://chronicle.com/blogs/buildings/sustainable-endowments-institute-suspends-green-report-card/31071\" target=\"_self\">Sustainable Endowments Institute Suspends Green Report Card</a></p>\r\n<h4>March 2012</h4>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://sustainablelafayette.org/?p=2789\" target=\"_self\">Saint Mary&rsquo;s College: A Sustainability Success Story in the Making</a></p>\r\n<h4>February 2012</h4>\r\n<p class=\"title\"><a href=\"http://www.environmentalleader.com/2012/02/03/tool-to-ease-colleges-reporting-for-sustainability-rankings/\" target=\"_self\">Tool to Ease Colleges\' Reporting for Sustainability Rankings</a><br /><a href=\"http://www.greenbiz.com/news/2012/02/02/greenest-colleges-rankings-get-easier-new-data-gathering-effort\" target=\"_self\">\'Greenest Colleg